  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  diabetes mellitus (1 or2)

          -  decreased vision from Diabetic Macular Edema (study eye Best Corrected Visual
             Acuity&lt;69 letters using E.T.D.R.S testing)

          -  macular edema

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  history of severe cardiac disease

          -  stroke within 12 months

          -  intraocular inflammation
      </textblock>
